name: Federal Bureau of Investigation
public_notes: Note: Ryan Shapiro provided fantastic tips on submitting FOIA requests to the FBI in his Requester's Voice interview. We highly recommend following Shapiro's suggestions of including "cross-reference" and "ELSUR (Electronic Surveillance)" search requests in your request language.

name: National Security Agency
public_notes: Questions about the status of a request may be sent to foiarsc@nsa.gov, but the Agency will not accept reqests via email as of the time of this writing.
